INSERT INTO comments (id, user_id, product_id, text, rating, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (35301, 25, 1126, 'EXCELLENT HIGH QUALITY THE DETACHABLE MIC The build quality is for its price Its made of durable plastic The ear cups can be turned great for casual wear it rests on your upper chest nicely its cushion also has this leatherlike material so it wont be breathable at least from my experience yet it fits perfectly with big ears and feels comfortable but maybe not suitable for long gaming sessions it might become sweaty It has a soft cushion on the headband so dont worry about the comfort on the top although its quite small The detachable mic is just perfect and easy to insert adjust The adjustable headband has levels on it so it locks on perfectly to your preferred comfort I put because of the ear cup cushion having this kind of almost coming off look at the back side idk if its intended or smth and also for the reason that it might break if a somewhat great force is applied to the headband its still made of plastic sooo Aesthetically I love the look the matte finish is nice for me and the shine on the JBL logo engraving on the cups is a nice touch The L R isnt seen when worn but I like the style its been printed in The detachable mic It really makes this product a gamingcasual wear headphones And being a nonwireless headphone the thin braided cord is not as conspicuous even with the hint of orange lines it has Functionality For its price the JBL Quantum s performance is excellent It doesnt have noise cancellation involved yet if you wear it you almost cant hear anything outside it The mic also sounds crispy although it is kinda lowvolume but it is still far better than using cheap earphone mics Volume is easy to adjust cause of the volume racks size and the no mic button near the volume rack is also a great addition for when you just want to listen to music or something For its price the JBL Quantum is an excellent product especially for budget gamers whore looking for a decent upgrade without overpaying for the k price range With your product having the JBL brand it is also a great flex for some heh for now Somewhat related story time At first I kinda doubted the products legitimacy I saw this same product posted on JBL Quantums official store here in Shopee but with a different price of k php So I went and asked the seller if this was genuine and also the reason why it was cheaper by php here Not long after the seller answered that all the products listed in their shop are original but did not answer the latter question Even with that question unanswered I still bought with a small doubt in mind and just believed and hoped that what I received was legit Fast forward a week after placing the order I got it I checked the box the warranty and the product itself Theyre all there its legit So if you have doubts about the legitimacy of their products here just ask the seller again or maybe ask for proof that its original and if you have lesser doubts buy it', 5, '2023-03-05 08:49:15', NULL);
